Hadoop based KNN/Query Computation

Packages
edu.ucsb.cs.knn Provides the driver class necessary to invoke the user choice of the job to be executed.
edu.ucsb.cs.knn.core Contains the basic implementation of fields and methods used accorss the project.
edu.ucsb.cs.knn.hybrid Contains the necessary Hadoop classes to execute the KNN on the original Yahoo songs data represented in forward indexing format.
edu.ucsb.cs.knn.inverted Contains the necessary Hadoop classes to execute the KNN on the songs datasets respresented in inverted indexing format.
edu.ucsb.cs.knn.preprocess Contains Hadoop classes to convert Yahoo music dataset into an inverted index of songs.
edu.ucsb.cs.knn.query Regular java program that fetches the KNN results as needed to predict the user rating for the input song query.
edu.ucsb.cs.knn.types Contains all the classes used as types in this project.
